## Basic Usage
### Pagination
Navigate through pages of data.
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="PaginationPaginationDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const page = ref(1)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxPagination
      v-model:current-page="page"
      :total="120"
      :page-size="10"
      show-info
      show-first-last
    />
  </template>
---
:::
